project-basis: With MongoDB, node.js, HTML, CSS, and lots of love.
project-challenges: I didn't know Node.js or MongoDB coming to this hackathon.
project-future-plans: We drop the space bit and compete with Imgur.
project-purpose: It stores your memes for you by allowing you to upload them to MongoDB queries and keep them there. Eventually, viewing is a feature to be added.
project-inspiration: When I upgraded to Windows 10, I almost lost all my memes. I wanted a place to keep them, exclusively for them, where I would never have to worry about them. The space part was a product of the Space hackathon.
project-accomplishments: Learning MongoDB and Node.js in a weekend. Sorta.
project-subtitle: Imgur, except primarily for storage and without a social aspect. And exclusively for space memes
